StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetCollegeVisitContactInfo]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@Organiza.onId int, @SchoolCode int, @FiscalYear int AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT [CollegeVisitContactId] ,C.[CollegeVisitContactTypeId] ,[LastName] ,[FirstName] ,[TelePhoneNumber] ,[Descrip.on] ,[Organiza.onId] ,[School_Code] AS SchoolCode ,[FiscalYear] ,[CellPhoneNumber] ,[EmailAddress] ,[LastUpdateUserId] FROM [MCRISS].[USMC].[CollegeVisitContact] C,[MCRISS].[USMC].CollegeVisitContactType CT
WHERE C.[CollegeVisitContactTypeId] = CT.[CollegeVisitContactTypeId] and C.[Organiza.onId] = @Organiza.onId and C.[School_Code] = @SchoolCode and C.[FiscalYear] = @FiscalYear
END
